      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Check out this dependable ride! It's a solid, functional vehicle that's perfect for someone looking for reliable transportation with a bit of character. While it shows some honest wear and tear from its years on the road, it still has plenty of life left and is ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for a budget-friendly option that gets the job done, this is the one for you!",
