      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this superlative vehicle, currently offered in showroom condition. Meticulously preserved and exhibiting no signs of wear, this specimen represents the pinnacle of its class. The exterior retains a deep, mirror-like finish, while the interior remains in an unblemished, factory-fresh state. Engineering excellence meets uncompromising maintenance in this rare find, suitable for the most discerning automotive enthusiast who requires perfection.",
      "price": 44800.0,
